thumbnail : "https://www.socialqueue.ai/opengraph-image.png"
snippet:"Open-source social media management tool"
---
Connect an unlimited number of social media accounts to that you want to post to from within Social Queue. Only drawback is that every post will have some text in the social media caption/title at the very end that says "posted via SocialQueue". 
Upgrading to the paid tier removes the watermark.
